54.4	John_Markoff	John Markoff	John Markoff (born October 24, 1949) is a journalist best known for his work at The New York Times, and a book and series of articles about the 1990s pursuit and capture of hacker Kevin Mitnick.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a1/John_Markoff.jpg/220px-John_Markoff.jpg
